<subSubSection id="DE5D6C5F4E30F37D0CAB90F5B4B8F380" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="4907D3097EA655353F7C31FF33F1B440" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B36FE407C4ACC0D4D69D4783E4D3A7A" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">
From Algeria to Iran (first record), south to Sudan and Saudi Arabia (
<bibRefCitation id="69DE93AA078179A9DA178BED4C521A0C" author="Spassky, SA" journalOrPublisher="Festschrift Embrik Strand" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" url="http://wsc.nmbe.ch" year="2018">WSC 2018</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
